questions.quote: You're right, you're right. I should just tell her the truth.
Are you crazy?! We own those two! I mean look at 'um, he can't breath and she's popping pills.
Look at me! I'm Chandler! Could I be wearing any more clothes? Maybe if I wasn't going commando...
There we go.You know what, if we were in prison, you guys would be, like, my bitches.
I'm sorry Chandler, y'know you are such a sweet guy and I, I don't want to hurt you. Oh, I wish there was something I can do to make you feel better.
Well, Monica and Chandler can't go. We're going to dinner remember?!
Oh! Oh, I just thought of the greatest wedding gift to get you.
Well, I think it all started when you said, "Hey Joey, why don't you be my best man."
I know I miss you too. I can't wait to see you. I love you. Bye.
Ohh, they gave me a great spot. Right by Macys. Yeah, they hardly ever give such a good spot to a rookie, but I'm the only one who can sing "Merry Christmas" in 25 languages. I lied.
